{
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "verse_number": 1,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:1",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "سَأَلَ سَآئِلُۢ بِعَذَابٖ وَاقِعٖ",
      "translation": "1. Alguien (de quienes niegan la fe) pide (desafiante) que se abata un castigo, que está a punto de suceder,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "verse_number": 2,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:2",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لِّلۡكَٰفِرِينَ لَيۡسَ لَهُۥ دَافِعٞ",
      "translation": "2. sobre quienes rechazan la verdad y que nadie podrá impedir,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "verse_number": 3,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:3",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "مِّنَ ٱللَّهِ ذِي ٱلۡمَعَارِجِ",
      "translation": "3. procedente de Al-lah, el Señor de las vías de ascensión (a los cielos). ",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "verse_number": 4,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:4",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "تَعۡرُجُ ٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ وَٱلرُّوحُ إِلَيۡهِ فِي يَوۡمٖ كَانَ مِقۡدَارُهُۥ خَمۡسِينَ أَلۡفَ سَنَةٖ",
      "translation": "4. A Él ascienden el ángel Gabriel[1075] y el resto de los ángeles en un día[1076]cuya duración equivale a cincuenta mil años (terrenales).",
      "footnotes": "[1075]  También puede significar que a Él ascienden los ángeles y las almas. \n[1076]   La mayoría de los comentaristas opinan que esta aleya hace alusión al Día de la Resurrección."
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "verse_number": 5,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:5",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَٱصۡبِرۡ صَبۡرٗا جَمِيلًا",
      "translation": "5. Sé paciente (¡oh, Muhammad!).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "verse_number": 6,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:6",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِنَّهُمۡ يَرَوۡنَهُۥ بَعِيدٗا",
      "translation": "6. Ellos ven (el castigo) muy lejano (como si nunca fuera a suceder),",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "verse_number": 7,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:7",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَنَرَىٰهُ قَرِيبٗا",
      "translation": "7. pero Nos lo vemos cercano.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "verse_number": 8,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:8",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يَوۡمَ تَكُونُ ٱلسَّمَآءُ كَٱلۡمُهۡلِ",
      "translation": "8. (Ocurrirá) el día en que el cielo adquirirá el color de los metales fundidos",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "verse_number": 9,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:9",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَتَكُونُ ٱلۡجِبَالُ كَٱلۡعِهۡنِ",
      "translation": "9. y las montañas parecerán lana cardada (por su inconsistencia),",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "verse_number": 10,
      "page_number": 568,
      "verse_key": "70:10",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَلَا يَسۡـَٔلُ حَمِيمٌ حَمِيمٗا",
      "translation": "10. y nadie preguntará por (la situación de) ningún ser querido, ",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "verse_number": 11,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:11",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يُبَصَّرُونَهُمۡۚ يَوَدُّ ٱلۡمُجۡرِمُ لَوۡ يَفۡتَدِي مِنۡ عَذَابِ يَوۡمِئِذِۭ بِبَنِيهِ",
      "translation": "11. a pesar de que podrán verse unos a otros. El pecador que rechazaba la verdad deseará librarse del castigo de la otra vida (entregando) a cambio a sus propios hijos,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "verse_number": 12,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:12",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَأَخِيهِ",
      "translation": "12. a su pareja y a su hermano,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "verse_number": 13,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:13",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَفَصِيلَتِهِ ٱلَّتِي تُـٔۡوِيهِ",
      "translation": "13. a la tribu que lo amparaba ",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "verse_number": 14,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:14",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَمَن فِي ٱلۡأَرۡضِ جَمِيعٗا ثُمَّ يُنجِيهِ",
      "translation": "14. y a todos los habitantes de la tierra, con tal de salvarse.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "verse_number": 15,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:15",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "كَلَّآۖ إِنَّهَا لَظَىٰ",
      "translation": "15. ¡De ningún modo! El fuego abrasador (será su castigo);",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "verse_number": 16,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:16",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "نَزَّاعَةٗ لِّلشَّوَىٰ",
      "translation": "16. le arrancará la piel de la cabeza y de todo el cuerpo.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "verse_number": 17,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:17",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "تَدۡعُواْ مَنۡ أَدۡبَرَ وَتَوَلَّىٰ",
      "translation": "17. (El fuego) llamará a quienes le dieron la espalda (a la fe) y se alejaron (de la verdad),",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "verse_number": 18,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:18",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 227,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَجَمَعَ فَأَوۡعَىٰٓ",
      "translation": "18. a quienes acumulaban riquezas y las atesoraban (sin dar nada en caridad ni contribuir a la causa de Al-lah).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "verse_number": 19,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:19",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "۞ إِنَّ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنَ خُلِقَ هَلُوعًا",
      "translation": "19. Ciertamente, el hombre fue creado impaciente e inestable:",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "verse_number": 20,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:20",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِذَا مَسَّهُ ٱلشَّرُّ جَزُوعٗا",
      "translation": "20. si se ve afectado por algún mal, se desespera;",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "verse_number": 21,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:21",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَإِذَا مَسَّهُ ٱلۡخَيۡرُ مَنُوعًا",
      "translation": "21. y cuando es agraciado con la fortuna, se vuelve mezquino;",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "verse_number": 22,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:22",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِلَّا ٱلۡمُصَلِّينَ",
      "translation": "22. salvo quienes realizan el salat",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "verse_number": 23,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:23",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَلَىٰ صَلَاتِهِمۡ دَآئِمُونَ",
      "translation": "23. con constancia",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "verse_number": 24,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:24",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ فِيٓ أَمۡوَٰلِهِمۡ حَقّٞ مَّعۡلُومٞ",
      "translation": "24. y dan de sus bienes una parte en caridad ",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "verse_number": 25,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:25",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لِّلسَّآئِلِ وَٱلۡمَحۡرُومِ",
      "translation": "25. a los mendigos y a los indigentes.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "verse_number": 26,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:26",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ يُصَدِّقُونَ بِيَوۡمِ ٱلدِّينِ",
      "translation": "26. Y quienes creen en el Día del Juicio Final",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "verse_number": 27,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:27",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ هُم مِّنۡ عَذَابِ رَبِّهِم مُّشۡفِقُونَ",
      "translation": "27. y temen el castigo de su Señor",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "verse_number": 28,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:28",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِنَّ عَذَابَ رَبِّهِمۡ غَيۡرُ مَأۡمُونٖ",
      "translation": "28. —realmente, nadie puede sentirse a salvo del castigo de su Señor—.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "verse_number": 29,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:29",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ لِفُرُوجِهِمۡ حَٰفِظُونَ",
      "translation": "29. Y quienes preservan su castidad,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "verse_number": 30,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:30",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِلَّا عَلَىٰٓ أَزۡوَٰجِهِمۡ أَوۡ مَا مَلَكَتۡ أَيۡمَٰنُهُمۡ فَإِنَّهُمۡ غَيۡرُ مَلُومِينَ",
      "translation": "30. salvo con sus esposas o con las esclavas que posean, pues no serán recriminados por ello.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "verse_number": 31,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:31",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَمَنِ ٱبۡتَغَىٰ وَرَآءَ ذَٰلِكَ فَأُوْلَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡعَادُونَ",
      "translation": "31. Y quienes busquen algo más allá de lo que les ha sido permitido serán unos transgresores.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "verse_number": 32,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:32",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ لِأَمَٰنَٰتِهِمۡ وَعَهۡدِهِمۡ رَٰعُونَ",
      "translation": "32. Y (también son una excepción) quienes devuelven lo que les ha sido confiado y cumplen sus compromisos;",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "verse_number": 33,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:33",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ هُم بِشَهَٰدَٰتِهِمۡ قَآئِمُونَ",
      "translation": "33. quienes mantienen sus testimonios con firmeza;",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "verse_number": 34,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:34",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلَّذِينَ هُمۡ عَلَىٰ صَلَاتِهِمۡ يُحَافِظُونَ",
      "translation": "34. y quienes realizan el salat (respetando su horario, sus condiciones y todos sus elementos).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "verse_number": 35,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:35",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ فِي جَنَّٰتٖ مُّكۡرَمُونَ",
      "translation": "35. Esos serán honrados en los jardines (del paraíso).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "verse_number": 36,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:36",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَمَالِ ٱلَّذِينَ كَفَرُواْ قِبَلَكَ مُهۡطِعِينَ",
      "translation": "36. Pero ¿qué les sucede a esos que rechazan la verdad y corren presurosos hacia ti",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "verse_number": 37,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:37",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "عَنِ ٱلۡيَمِينِ وَعَنِ ٱلشِّمَالِ عِزِينَ",
      "translation": "37. en grupos (¡oh, Muhammad!) y se sitúan a tu derecha y a tu izquierda (y se burlan de los creyentes diciendo que si estos entran en el paraíso, ellos lo harán antes)?",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "verse_number": 38,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:38",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَيَطۡمَعُ كُلُّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ أَن يُدۡخَلَ جَنَّةَ نَعِيمٖ",
      "translation": "38. ¿Acaso piensan todos ellos que entrarán en el jardín de las delicias?",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "verse_number": 39,
      "page_number": 569,
      "verse_key": "70:39",
      "juz_number": 29,
      "hizb_number": 57,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 228,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "كَلَّآۖ إِنَّا خَلَقۡنَٰهُم مِّمَّا يَعۡلَمُونَ",
      "translation": "39. ¡De ningún modo! Realmente, los creamos a partir de lo que ya saben[1077].",
      "footnotes": "[1077]  Al-lah les recuerda que no son superiores a los creyentes y que fueron creados, como el resto de los hombres, de una insignificante cantidad de esperma eyaculada."
